## 5. raw#10 honest C3

1. **cemiplimab Libtayo 2018** = first FDA PD-1 cSCC — metastatic + locally advanced. cSCC 가 melanoma 다음 두번째 PD-1 표적 cutaneous malignancy. 양자-VQE 의 PD-1 pocket fit 직접 fit (cross-melanoma_specific + 만성 결합).
2. **pembrolizumab Keytruda 2020** = second FDA PD-1 cSCC. R/R + locally advanced. Keytruda broad oncology umbrella 의 cSCC 적응증 확장.
3. **tirbanibulin Klisyri 2020** = first FDA tubulin inhibitor AK. 5-day course — 만성 imiquimod 4-week + 5-FU 2-week 보다 짧음. compliance 향상.
4. **ingenol mebutate Picato withdrawn 2020** = PKC activator topical AK — EMA withdrawal 2020 carcinogenicity 신호. paradigm lessons: short-course efficacy 가 long-term safety 와 trade-off.
5. **mTOR (sirolimus/everolimus) transplant cSCC** = transplant immunosuppression-induced cSCC 2차예방. cyclosporine/tacrolimus → sirolimus switch 가 cSCC 위험 감소 + 만성 immunosuppression 변경 (cross-transplant).
6. **Mohs micrographic surgery (MMS)** = 만성 표준 head/neck high-risk cSCC. 99% margin clearance. tissue-sparing + cosmetic 결과 + recurrence 감소.
7. **PDT (ALA/MAL + light)** = photodynamic therapy AK + cSCC in situ. tumor-selective photosensitizer + light activation. surgery 회피 + cosmetic 결과.
8. **5-FU + imiquimod + diclofenac topical AK** = 만성 1st-line topical AK. 5-FU pyrimidine antimetabolite + imiquimod TLR7 agonist + diclofenac NSAID. mechanism 다양성.
9. **SPF + sun avoidance 1차예방** = 만성 1차예방 (cross-melanoma_specific + climate_health). UV cumulative damage 가 cSCC + AK 의 main driver. 한국 K-SPF labeling 식약처 framework.
10. **wet-lab + clinical RCT 없음** — quantum-only in-silico, cSCC + AK 임상 의미 한정.

